title: Dragon NaturallySpeaking For Dummies
description:
2013 | 384 Pages | ISBN: 1118671252 | EPUB  PDF | 10 MB  34 MB

Learn to speak Dragon with For Dummies!

Fully updated for the latest speech recognition tools and features, this bestselling guide helps you conquer Dragon NaturallySpeaking and gets you started creating documents, sending e-mail, searching the web, and more using only your voice.

You?ll learn Dragon basics like dictation, formatting, and proofreading before moving on to more advanced options including posting to social media sites, developing custom commands, troubleshooting, and improving communication with Dragon.
